<<ContentPage.Padding> <OnPlatform x:TypeArguments="Thickness"> <On Platform="iOS" Value="20, 40, 20, 20" /> <On Platform="Android, WinPhone, Windows" Value="20" /> </OnPlatform> </ContentPage.Padding> <AbsoluteLayout> <Grid> <Grid.RowDefinitions> <RowDefinition Height="*" /> <RowDefinition Height="*" /> <RowDefinition Height="*" /> <RowDefinition Height="*" /> <RowDefinition Height="*" /> <RowDefinition Height="*" /> </Grid.RowDefinitions> <Grid.ColumnDefinitions> <ColumnDefinition Width="120" /> <ColumnDefinition Width="*" /> </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
<Label Text="Weather" HorizontalOptions="StartAndExpand" VerticalOptions="Start" FontSize="18" TextColor="White" Grid.Row="0" /> <Label Text="{Binding CurrentTime}" HorizontalOptions="Center" VerticalOptions="Start" FontSize="15" TextColor="White" Grid.Row="1" Grid.ColumnSpan="2"/>
<Image Source="{Binding Icon}" Grid.Row="3" Grid.Column="0" Scale="2"/>
<Label Text="{Binding TempMax, StringFormat='Max {0}&##186;C'}" Grid.Row="3" Grid.Column="1" HorizontalOptions="End" FontSize="25" TextColor="White" /> <Label Text="{Binding TempMin, StringFormat='Min {0}&##186;C'}" Grid.Row="4" Grid.Column="1" HorizontalOptions="End" FontSize="15" TextColor="White" Opacity="0.5"/> <Label Text="{Binding Location}" Grid.Row="5" Grid.ColumnSpan="2" FontSize="18" TextColor="White" HorizontalOptions="Center" VerticalOptions="End"/>
</Grid> <ActivityIndicator IsRunning="{Binding IsBusy}" Color="Aqua" AbsoluteLayout.LayoutBounds="0.5, 0.5, 100, 100" AbsoluteLayout.LayoutFlags="PositionProportional"/>
</AbsoluteLayout>.../>
